headline: Public Storage: Solid REIT To Watch, But Don't Ignore The Preferred Stock
summary: Public Storage has 9.7% FAD growth and $1.3B in 2025 projects as preferred shares yield 6% and debt costs rise. Find out why PSA stock is a hold.
